# Implementation Plan - Project AssetFlow (Stage 4 -> Stage 5)

Transition the application to a production-ready single-server architecture and implement direct Microsoft Graph API cloud integration.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - We will modify `main.py` to serve the React `dist` folder. This means you must run `npm run build` before the backend can serve the frontend.
> - Direct MS Graph API integration requires specific app permissions (`Files.ReadWrite.All`) in your Entra ID portal.
> - We are implementing a "Single Server" model to facilitate `.exe` packaging later.

